## React Rules

### Component Structure
- Sử dụng functional components với TypeScript
- Props interface rõ ràng
- Default props khi cần
- Memoization với React.memo khi cần

### Hooks
- Sử dụng custom hooks cho business logic
- Proper dependency arrays
- Cleanup effects
- Error handling trong hooks

### State Management
- useState cho local state
- useReducer cho complex state
- Zustand cho global state
- Proper state updates

### Event Handling
- Proper event types
- useCallback cho performance
- Prevent default behavior
- Error boundaries

### Styling
- Tailwind CSS classes
- Responsive design
- Consistent spacing
- Dark mode support